snippet.title: Red's Revenge Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Demo available on Itch.io! 

You've been hired to power wash a recently renovated hospital. The owners recently bought the hospital after it was abandoned for several years. The renovations are nearly complete, however, teenagers are somehow sneaking in at night and putting up graffiti. This job should cover this months rent...

Will you finish the job and escape with your life?
